&lt;Info-Data Inc> said itwill acquire &lt;USA Outdoor Advertising Inc> of Jacksonville,Fla., in exchange for stock.    USA Outdoor Advertising was acquired for 62.4 pct of theoutstanding shares of Info-Data Inc, the company said.    Info-Data said it plans to change its name to USA OutdoorAdvertising Inc to reflect the change in the company'soperations. Reuter&#3;